{"tid":644880,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)死囚大逃殺 逃獄三王 石破天驚","createTime":"2018-04-27T14:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T19:15:12.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9221278a583b806722fc1497f97a49755e4e2c5","tid":644880,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=0dcvmh6q41fXOr6Ir49lS9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9e69c3b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=0dcvmh6q41fXOr6Ir49lS9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=08568e2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=0dcvmh6q41fXOr6Ir49lS9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=656d95b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/32zKlzYXjM9zs00P85k5dn9G3Lb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.tmdb.org%2Ft%2Fp%2Foriginal%2F32zKlzYXjM9zs00P85k5dn9G3Lb.jpg&h=3888bf26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/5b/O_brother_where_art_thou_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5b%2FO_brother_where_art_thou_ver1.jpg&h=0aed7b61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/danlkaelb/1320245400-901803871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fdanlkaelb%2F1320245400-901803871.jpg&h=d94dd39e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.傑克&middot;康拉德是一名死刑犯，正在美國中部的一個監獄中等待著最後時刻。不料卻被腐敗的獄方賣給有錢的電視制作人，被迫參加一個非法的生死遊戲真人秀。傑克被帶到了一個與外界隔絕的孤島上，他發現這場遊戲的參賽者除了自己還有其他九個人，都是來自世界不同地方的死囚。他們彼此必須竭盡全力展開生死搏鬥，因爲只有最後生存下來的人才有機會重獲自由。想逃走根本是不可能的事，他們的一舉一動都通過網絡向數百萬觀衆直播。康拉德必須使出渾身解數，贏得生存和自由的唯一機會&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.30年代初，密西西比州荒野的監獄裡，一群&ldquo;勞改犯&rdquo;正乾著枯燥，繁重的採石，碎石的活計嘮嘮叨叨，油嘴滑舌的艾弗瑞特（喬治&middot;克魯尼飾）也是其中 在一個破壞石頭上，整天打著各種逃跑的鬼主意。在成功說服了難點頭腦簡單的德爾瑪（蒂姆&middot;布雷克&middot;尼爾森飾）和相當 大膽的皮特（約翰&middot;特托羅飾）之後，艾弗瑞特的越獄大計終於得以實現，三個穿著犯人服，拖著手銬，腳鐐的罪叮叮叮噹當地踏上了通往自由和寶藏的路途<br />\n<br />\n3.在1963年以前，位於舊金山外海的惡魔島以嚴密的警衛措施，成為全美犯人聞之喪膽的魔鬼監獄，固若金湯的天牢設計，讓重刑犯如同囚禁在銅牆鐵壁之中。監獄廢棄後，惡魔島成了觀光勝地，每日都有遊客湧進其中，嘗試坐牢的滋味。然而此時惡魔島卻落在一群軍人的手裡，成為他們臨時的基地<br />\n<br />\n11 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=0dcvmh6q41fXOr6Ir49lS9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7bb88eb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=0dcvmh6q41fXOr6Ir49lS9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=cd81f405\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42578cca033f801fd1c7c45234950db848336041","tid":644880,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c39a621b0826c724b6c3a2daba8357c8bfb4f3","tid":644880,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7feafb645577e389cf1626f7a11185f67db8cda9","tid":644880,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbcc3b149ae7de39ff6be337ff4306f04f41fd9","tid":644880,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435f7bf8b4f868c11dade3c85a2cb0832347a49d","tid":644880,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T18:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bf16186c7dd55e2148d0b03af763fe904303ea","tid":644880,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T19:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}